These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-1::.
City: london, san-francisco, miami
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, azalea, dahlia
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, september, april
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, brown, lilac
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the person who growsbellflower and the person who likes ebony##2
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
3. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
4. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
6. the person who growsbellflower is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| City          | london      | san-francisco        | miami     |
| Flower         | dahlia | azalea | bellflower    |
| Birthday   | september   | february       | april |
| Color         | ebony  | brown      | lilac    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, white, mauve
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, tea, lemonade
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, begonia, balloon-flower
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, traveling, sudoku
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person drinking tea is the person who likes white##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
4. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3
6. the person who likes mauve is in an even position##4
7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person drinking tea and the person who likes blood-red##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| Color           | white    | mauve | blood-red |
| Beverage   | tea | 7up       | lemonade   |
| Flower           | balloon-flower  | begonia   | daisy     |
| Hobby         | traveling | sudoku       | skydiving   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: british, french, japanese
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, aquamarine, ivory
House: gothic-revival, palace, art-deco
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, july, august
1. the art-deco house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the japanese is the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the french is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
4. the british is between the person who likes aquamarine and the person who's birthday is in august##2
5. the person who likes azure is in an even position##4
6. the art-deco house is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Nationality          | japanese | british | french |
| Color   | ivory     | azure | aquamarine |
| House           | palace       | gothic-revival   | art-deco    |
| Birthday     | august      | march   | july |

