.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-4::.
3 different games are played: canasta, mah-jongg, whist
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, alhambra, cain
There 3 different types of food: radish, cucumber, grapes
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, azalea, daffodil
1. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3
2. the person eating radish is on the left of the person playing whist##1
3. the cain-smoker is the person eating cucumber##1
4. the person who growsazalea is on the far right##1
5. the game-smoker is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
6. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
7. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3      |
| Game         | mah-jongg  | canasta       | whist |
| Cigar           | cain     | alhambra      | game   |
| Food   | cucumber | radish | grapes     |
| Flower   | sunflower      | daffodil   | azalea     |

