.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-5::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, black, ebony
3 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, whist
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, hiking, camping
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, tennis, badminton
1. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who likes black##1
3. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
5. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
6. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who likes black##1
7. the person who's sport is badminton is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3        |
| Color      | ebony     | black   | white         |
| Game           | snooker | scrabble | whist |
| Hobby   | camping      | hiking   | video-games            |
| Sport   | tennis   | badminton  | ice-hockey         |

