.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, cycling, handball
City: rome, hannover, colone
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, daisy, begonia
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, december, august
1. the person who growsdaisy is between the person traveling to hannover and the person who's sport is cycling##2
2. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person who growsbegonia is the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |
| Sport          | handball    | weightlifting     | cycling |
| City           | hannover | colone | rome      |
| Flower   | begonia      | daisy       | bellflower    |
| Birthday   | december      | july         | august     |

