City: paris, miami, colone
3 different games are played: scrabble, poker, go
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, cola, juice
1. the project-manager is in the middle##1
2. the person playing poker is on the left of the project-manager##1
3. the person traveling to colone is the person drinking cola##1
4. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
5. the nurse is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
6. the person playing scrabble is between the person drinking cola and the lawyer##2
7. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Job          | lawyer | project-manager | nurse |
| City   | miami  | paris    | colone |
| Game   | poker  | scrabble   | go    |
| Beverage     | juice   | soy-milk       | cola |

