.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-8::.
House: art-deco, ranch-style, colonial
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, swimming, baseball
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, zinnia, rose
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, metal, r&b
1. the person who growsrose is on the far left or far right##3
2. the colonial house is on the far right##1
3. the ranch-style house is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
6. the fan of soul is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person who growszinnia and the fan of r&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |
| House      | ranch-style | art-deco    | colonial  |
| Sport         | baseball        | sailing   | swimming   |
| Flower   | rose       | bellflower    | zinnia |
| Music-Genre     | r&b          | metal | soul       |

