2. the person watching sports movies is in an even position##4
3. the person drinking soy-milk is the old-henry-smoker##1
4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
6. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
