.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, water
3 different pets are kept: horse, goldfish, turtle
3 different games are played: canasta, billiard, go
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, tulip, azalea
1. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the owner of the horse is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person drinking water is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the owner of the horse is the person playing go##1
5. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
6. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
7. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage           | sprite     | water    | tea |
| Pet   | horse  | goldfish | turtle      |
| Game   | go       | billiard   | canasta    |
| Flower     | tulip | azalea        | daisy     |

