3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4
5. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
6. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
7. the colonial house is the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3       |
