.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-12::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, march, may
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, disco, techno
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, marigold, zinnia
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, chess, collecting
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
2. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
3. the person who growszinnia is on the far right##1
4. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
5. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
6. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
7. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who growslily##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Birthday      | may       | march   | july |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | techno     | disco |
| Flower           | lily      | marigold | zinnia    |
| Hobby         | chess  | collecting     | gardening |

