.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-13::.
House: farmhouse, wooden, modern
There 3 different types of food: cranberry, kiwi, tomato
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, country, electronic
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, horror, fantasy
1. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
2. the farmhouse house is on the left of the wooden house##1
3. the wooden house is in an even position##4
4. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is the person watching fantasy movies##1
6. the person eating kiwi is in the middle##1
7. the person watching horror movies is on the far left##1
8. the fan of country is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
9. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| House           | farmhouse | wooden   | modern |
| Food   | cranberry  | kiwi    | tomato    |
| Music-Genre         | country    | hip-hop | electronic   |
| Movie-Genre     | horror  | fantasy     | animation  |

