3 different games are played: backgammon, billiard, whist
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cabbage, pomegranate
House: cottage, modern, victorian
1. the person eating carrot is the game-smoker##1
2. the victorian house is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the cottage house is in an odd position##4
4. the modern house is between the person playing whist and the baccarat-smoker##2
5. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
6. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the victorian house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |      3       |
| Cigar         | game    | montecristo   | baccarat      |
| Game           | whist | backgammon    | billiard |
| Food   | carrot       | cabbage | pomegranate      |
| House         | victorian         | modern   | cottage     |

