.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-19::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, orange, blood-red
3 different games are played: chess, monopoly, mah-jongg
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, alhambra, chaman
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, fishing, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an odd position##4
2. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who likes blood-red##1
5. the chaman-smoker is in an even position##4
6. the person playing chess is the alhambra-smoker##1
7. the bongani-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who likes orange is the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |
| Color          | orange  | brown   | blood-red |
| Game   | monopoly      | mah-jongg      | chess   |
| Cigar   | bongani     | chaman | alhambra |
| Hobby         | fishing | card-games   | traveling   |

