House: gothic-revival, palace, tower
1. the tower house is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
3. the russian is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
4. the palace house is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
6. the person who growstulip is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2        |     3      |
| Flower           | begonia  | tulip | poppy   |
| Nationality   | australian | russian           | nigerian      |
| Hobby           | reading   | gardening          | video-games |
| House     | gothic-revival    | tower           | palace |

 